Source: West Coast Times
Author:
Vol / Page: 2
Edition:
Quote: The foregoing is the title of an exhaustive paper written by Dr Teichelmann, which appears in the New Zealand Graphic Christmas number, with numerous illustrations from photographs taken by the Doctor on his annual mountaineering trips. The author's purpose is chiefly to show that the approach to the Southern Alps from the West Coast side is through more interesting country than from the Eastern side, and that the route is most accessible.
